# Mini Design Canvas Editor — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A fully-featured design canvas editor with a premium dark UI, deployed locally at `http://localhost:5173/`.

## Screenshots

![Initial State](file:///C:/Users/Aniket/.gemini/antigravity/brain/0b9dcb18-a1d9-4a62-bee8-ffd354aa5e4e/initial_canvas_view_1772731427707.png)
*Clean initial state — dark grid background, white canvas, left toolbar, right panel*

![Rectangle selected with properties](file:///C:/Users/Aniket/.gemini/antigravity/brain/0b9dcb18-a1d9-4a62-bee8-ffd354aa5e4e/rectangle_properties_1772732119509.png)
*Rectangle selected with 8 resize handles + Properties panel showing position, color, border radius, opacity, layer controls, duplicate & delete*

## Features Implemented

| Feature | Status | Details |
|---|---|---|
| Canvas Workspace | ✅ | 900×600px white board on dark grid |
| Element Creation | ✅ | Rectangle, Text, Image (click canvas after selecting tool) |
| Element Selection | ✅ | 8 resize handles (corners + edges), purple outline |
| Drag Movement | ✅ | Pointer capture for smooth drag |
| Resize | ✅ | All 8 directional handles |
| Layer Management | ✅ | z-index ordering, Layers tab shows all elements |
| Element Deletion | ✅ | Delete/Backspace key or panel button |
| Undo/Redo | ✅ | Ctrl+Z / Ctrl+Shift+Z + topbar buttons |
| Duplicate | ✅ | Ctrl+D or Duplicate button |
| Properties Panel | ✅ | Position, size, color, font, opacity, border radius |
| Text Editing | ✅ | Double-click to edit text in-place |
| Export PNG | ✅ | html2canvas exports the board |
| GitHub Push | ✅ | https://github.com/Aniketbisht31/GDGTASK.git |

